        <abstract>
            <p>Thinks GHL’s articles are quite excellent; hopes they will be republished.</p>
            <p>Discusses adaptation. Doubts whether similar conditions without selection can produce similar organs independent of blood relationship: "resemblances due to descent and adaptation can commonly be distinguished".</p>
            <p>Discusses luminous insects, electrical organs of fish, thorns and spines.</p>
        </abstract>
